    "passive": {
      "name": "Siphon Starlium",
      "description": "Ixia's Basic Attacks and skills apply a stack of (Starlium Charge) to enemies on hit. When Ixia performs a Basic Attack on an enemy with two stacks of (Starlium Charge), the attack will consume the stacks and be replaced with (Siphon Starlium), dealing ( +150% Total Physical Attack) (+20000% Lifesteal) plus (+10*Hero Level) (Physical Damage) to the target. Ixia recovers HP equal to the damage dealt by (Siphon Starlium) (only 20(+10000% Lifesteal)% against non-hero units). (Siphon Starlium) can trigger on all enemies in front of Ixia that are within her Basic Attack range, but it cannot Crit. Ixia's Basic Attacks cannot trigger Lifesteal.",
